{"title": "Parliament Approves the New Director General for NWRMA", "html": "<section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_medium sidebar-fix\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1 class=\"w-post-elm post_title us_custom_d503c3f4 entry-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">Parliament Approves the New Director General for NWRMA</h1><div class=\"w-hwrapper align_left valign_top wrap\"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date us_custom_ea2be81a entry-date published\" datetime=\"2025-11-11T02:00:34+00:00\" title=\"11 November 2025 at 02:00:34 +00:00\" itemprop=\"datePublished\"><span class=\"w-post-elm-before\">Posted on </span>11 Nov 2025</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments us_custom_ea2be81a layout_amount color_link_inherit with_word\"><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/parliament-approves-the-new-director-general-for-nwrma/#respond\">No Comments</a></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_small\"></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_image us_custom_70facfb4 stretched\"><img width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2026/01/580989521_1345186810951397_4152158779342178514_n.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2026/01/580989521_1345186810951397_4152158779342178514_n.jpg 2048w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2026/01/580989521_1345186810951397_4152158779342178514_n-300x200.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2026/01/580989521_1345186810951397_4152158779342178514_n-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2026/01/580989521_1345186810951397_4152158779342178514_n-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" /></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content\" itemprop=\"text\"><p>The new Director General, Ing. Pierre Palmer has been approved by Parliament as the successor to the outgoing Director General, Junisa Patrick Bangali Esq., who steered the Agency&#8217;s operations since its inception in 2019.<br />\nIng Palmer brings a wealth of experience to the office, as he served as Community Services Manager at Guma Valley Water Company. He has been in the water sector for over sixteen years.<br />\nHe holds a bachelor&#8217;s degree, in Civil Engineering from the University of Sierra Leone, a master&#8217;s degree, in Integrated Water Resources Management from Australia, and many other professional certificates.<br />\nMeet Ing. Palmer, the new Director General of the National Water Resources Management Agency</p>\n</div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium\"></div><div class=\"w-sharing type_solid align_left color_default\"><div class=\"w-sharing-list\" data-sharing-url=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl/parliament-approves-the-new-director-general-for-nwrma/\" data-sharing-image=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2026/01/580989521_1345186810951397_4152158779342178514_n-1024x683.jpg\"><a class=\"w-sharing-item email\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"Email this\" aria-label=\"Email this\"><span class=\"w-sharing-icon\"></span></a><a class=\"w-sharing-item facebook\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"Share this\" aria-label=\"Share this\"><span class=\"w-sharing-icon\"></span></a><a class=\"w-sharing-item twitter\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"Tweet this\" aria-label=\"Tweet this\"><span class=\"w-sharing-icon\"></span></a><a class=\"w-sharing-item linkedin\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"Share this\" aria-label=\"Share this\"><span class=\"w-sharing-icon\"></span></a><a class=\"w-sharing-item pinterest\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"Pin this\" aria-label=\"Pin this\"><span class=\"w-sharing-icon\"></span></a><a class=\"w-sharing-item vk\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"Share this\" aria-label=\"Share this\"><span class=\"w-sharing-icon\"></span></a></div></div><div c